Main URL: http://{server_ip}/hahiti

Client-Server Contract:

    Action    |     HTTP Method      |     URL
-------------------------------------------------------
Add User      |  PUT                 |  /users/{id}
Remove User   |  DELETE              |  /users/{id}
Get User      |  GET                 |  /users/{id}
Add Group     |  PUT                 |  /groups/{id}
Remove Group  |  DELETE              |  /groups/{id}
Get Group     |  GET                 |  /groups/{id}
